Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.75,0:01:03.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:13.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.04,0:01:20.20,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.01,0:01:28.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剪刀、石頭、布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.23,0:01:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.52,0:02:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第二話  自我風格」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(各位早安 又是熊本時間了 首先報導幻獸情報)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(熊本管區的梅倉小姐)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(這裏是熊本管區 八代地區災害慘重)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水同學\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(巨型且強大的6號幻獸)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣的東西就可以吧\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(昨日已消滅 車輛進出限制解除)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.91,0:03:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想說你應該快來了 所以早就準備好咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(損失報告日後司令部會擇日公開)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天真的是辛苦你了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(以上是熊本管區的報導)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧你們打倒怪獸 今年的中元也能好好辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是很感謝你們呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(謝謝 也祝各位有美好一天)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我差不多該上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天也會等你來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.01,0:03:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本節目是由為人類開拓未來的芝村關係企業所提供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水又輸了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正平常都是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥時的速水同學感覺如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時我都已經自顧不暇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以沒注意到其他人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原學姊 你對那樣的人有興趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺很能引起母性本能呢～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-所以注意上他了？\N- 一點點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼行 原學姊你已經有我了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位同學 這似乎不適合當成早上的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壬生屋你臉紅了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.16,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未央 什麼是母性本能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-好像這樣咯\N-好乖好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不純潔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未央 怎麼不理我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壬生屋比較硬 學姊比較軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣會癢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是同性之戀吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是女同性戀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼？好吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別裝傻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是香蕉口味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-喂喂 剛剛吞下去了？\N-還蠻好喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是田邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就是62勝6敗 勝率超過九成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為什麼贏不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你的賭運太差啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外還會是怎樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-喂 還我啦\N-有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-上面寫了什麼啊\N-自己看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是女孩子的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些未成年的不要管啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.93,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得你在轉移話題 不過這是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們吵死啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}現在報導八代地區臨時對應中心提供的被害情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.25,0:05:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}7月8日為止 幻獸6號造成305人死亡 523人輕重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}失蹤者有800人以上 目前仍在持續調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.26,0:06:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}關於死者身份的指認 請詢問各地緊急事故應對單位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,袖子好像有點長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.98,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正還會長大 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 臨時轉學過來真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍中好像沒在說轉學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.56,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是抱歉 我負責普通科 所以不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家回位子上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 現在介紹新朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天成為各位同學的芝村舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 是不是那個芝村集團…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不就是有錢人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定只是姓氏一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位同學請安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那芝村同學就坐那邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就開始上課了 請大家打開課本吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(芝村舞 外型漂亮)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…芝村同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的話 由我來帶你熟悉這個環境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要順便吃個飯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.90,0:08:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(法式料理？意式料理？還是中華或日本料理？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.91,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的開場白真是老套呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我們好好聊一聊吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.61,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會太積極了啊\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(剛轉學過來 很多事都不熟悉吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-他在說什麼啊\N-沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我們這樣的學生煩惱也多 我很想成為你的助力)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 他也這樣跟我說過\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(在這黑暗的時代裏)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(人跟人之間都要相互扶持)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊也被他這樣說過啊 真是意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你別無誤會 這話我可都沒跟任何人說過喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你也可以感覺到 這都是命運)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是分離而孤單的靈魂會彼此吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你也跟我一樣寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提醒芝村同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個男人是看到女生就會開始飢渴的色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.99,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學術名是哺乳類泡妞目好色科的瀨戶口色狼隆之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很危險 遭受毒爪的女孩多不可數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守備範圍從小孩到老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.66,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不是男生都沒問題 即使是宇宙人也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你們啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.68,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們班上的女生說話比較毒 這些都是開玩笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村同學 你願意相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村同學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的訓練是基於有新駕駛員的加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以由兩人一組 進行雙人座HWT操作適應訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.22,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本訓練的重點在於雙方的默契跟合作程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.06,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-請務必記得這一點\N-遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼首先由芝村同學跟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨戶口有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我目前的身心狀況都是巔峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我現在的使命感 可是比那阿蘇山的溶漿還炎熱)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了呢 這才像是瀨戶口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能藉這個機會 展現我的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就先由芝村跟瀨戶口開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟動主系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,索敵雷達跟炮火管制系統正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假想敵設定記錄開啟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有系統沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訓練開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村座機成功打倒幻獸哥魯戈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我是瀨戶口)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(要一起去看電影嗎？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(還是去游泳池玩？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(還是圖書館比較好？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.32,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(小舞有聽到嗎？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冒失傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 你打錯對像咯\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(連生氣的樣子也好可愛喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你的愛情表現還真激烈啊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.46,0:12:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-她比壬生屋還厲害呢\N-瀨戶口真可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水 剛剛的聲音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.98,0:13:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這樣就要對她道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是既然她幫了我們 還是道謝一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.35,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太喜歡那個人 總覺得她好像很難以接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.12,0:13:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真稀奇的組合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-兩個人要準備約會？\N-不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.13,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被壬生屋甩掉的話 隨時都可以來找姊姊我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會隨時安慰你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先走咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村同學她沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她看起來很內向不是嗎 而且幾乎都沒有說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擔心她能不能跟大家好好相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的個性其實很活潑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說瀨戶口的事情了 這對他也算是個教訓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話 還是呆呆的人比較好\N啊 我指的就是速水同學啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他看起來總是漫不經心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不要隨便跟別人說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是全部了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你睡覺不用棉被嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有一起送來 不過好像還沒送到的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我把睡衣跟睡袋借你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就重新自我介紹 我的名字是加藤祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責5121部隊的經理裝備跟文書工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼其他的事情也可以找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.58,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛的說明費 特價算你五百塊就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在身上沒這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑、開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用付也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得對話有些不搭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.36,0:15:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村舞 我總有一天要追到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲音太大咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訓練輸給她有這麼挫折嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對要讓她迷上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種女孩哪裏好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才一定要征服她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,征服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.99,0:15:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在的內心正不斷燃燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-瀧川\N-幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在知道你之前所說內心燃燒的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-所以就跟我一起燃燒吧\N-瀨戶口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧 芝村舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我叫做速水\N-我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.16,0:16:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天救我們的是芝村同學沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實壬生屋應該也要來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是盡軍人的義務罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那畢竟是我的失誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.95,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為害你也遭受危險 所以想來跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對、對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.09,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要道歉之前先把工作做好 會失誤的話就多努力點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要沒事就嘻皮笑臉的 或是隨便向別人低頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你為什麼要道歉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是因為這樣 所以才會被說是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.84,0:16:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呆呆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問呆呆是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 是男人就果斷一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 那我告辭了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.22,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是很感謝你的幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(現在報導八代地區的被害狀況)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.23,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(目前仍在搜尋失蹤民眾 不過作業似乎遇到瓶頸)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美 今天真早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.75,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎是嗎 多吃點 趕快長大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跌倒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.04,0:17:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以坐這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問小舞是大功臣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.95,0:18:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大功臣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.11,0:18:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你救了小志跟未央啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就是大功臣咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不記得說過你救過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不記得有救過你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以吵架啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在生氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.35,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師說未央不太懂禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過未央是望望美的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小舞也要跟她好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真紀你看 好多泡泡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.86,0:18:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣 會沾到眼睛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太懂禮貌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.89,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我以前用的尺寸 不太合就別太在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 那就明天見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加藤同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我祭就可以了 你那樣叫我會不好意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.05,0:19:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太善於跟別人說話 不知道大家會不會覺得我很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家應該都不會介意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我雖然很喜歡說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過要我注意說話細節 我一定會受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.67,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況我們班本來就都是些奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小布 吃飯羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛去哪裏了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
